A couple of differences, and some minutiae on print not visible on mark, but this is explainable due to distortion and the surface interruptions (vertical black line). All the stars I have marked are located around the area of the black line. The line is obscuring what I can see, and making things look slightly different. All other minutiae are fairly clear, with a couple of extra marked up at comparison stage. 
Core is roughly where I expected it to be as this was a guess at analysis stage. 

Degree of support - 4 (would more lean towards a 5 but I didn't mark as a high degree of discriminability initially)
